<p>The following parts of the Netcompany Foundation is showcased in this application:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Domain Driven Design (DDD)</li>
    <li>Command-Query Separation (CQS)</li>
    <li>Dependency Injection</li>
    <li>Code-first using Entity Framework Core (EF)</li>
    <li>Unit-test using xUnit</li>
</ul>

